fields.#productname: OGX Sea Salt Waves Shampoo 385ml
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
Information

Drag to spin

General Information

From Bondi to Broome, this beach-inspired blend with sea salt, sea kelp and aloe extract helps to rehydrate and condition parched strands. This texturizing formula helps add body and create the look of tousled beach hair all year round. Extend those beach vibes no matter the season with the scent of ocean air and sea salt in your hair!

Why you want it... For hair that gives you all the beach vibes!

Size: 385mL

Scent: Sea Salt Waves

Warnings

Avoid contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately. In case of any discomfort, please discontinue and consult a physician. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Water, Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Glycerin, Polyquaternium-22, PEG-7 Amodimethicone, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Citrate, Linoleamidopropyl PG-Dimonium Chloride Phosphate, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Disodium EDTA, Polyquatemium-39, PEG-150 Pentaerythrityl Tetrastearate, PPG-2 Hydroxyethyl Cocamide, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Macrocystis Pyrifera (Kelp) Extract, Maltodextrin/VP Copolymer, PVP, Sea Salt, Sodium Hydroxide, CI 60730, Hexylene Glycol.

Directions

What You Do... Apply Shampoo generously to wet hair, massage into a lather through to ends, then rinse the hair thoroughly. After shampooing, follow with conditioner. For best results, use in conjunction with other OGX products.

This texturizing formula helps add body and create the look of tousled beach hair all year round. Extend those beach vibes no matter the season with the scent of ocean air and sea salt in your hair!

Why you want it... For hair that gives you all the beach vibes!

Size: 385mL

Scent: Sea Salt Waves

Warnings

Avoid contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately. In case of any discomfort, please discontinue and consult a physician. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Water, Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Glycerin, Polyquaternium-22, PEG-7 Amodimethicone, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Citrate, Linoleamidopropyl PG-Dimonium Chloride Phosphate, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Disodium EDTA, Polyquatemium-39, PEG-150 Pentaerythrityl Tetrastearate, PPG-2 Hydroxyethyl Cocamide, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Macrocystis Pyrifera (Kelp) Extract, Maltodextrin/VP Copolymer, PVP, Sea Salt, Sodium Hydroxide, CI 60730, Hexylene Glycol.

Directions

What You Do... Apply Shampoo generously to wet hair, massage into a lather through to ends, then rinse the hair thoroughly. After shampooing, follow with conditioner. For best results, use in conjunction with other OGX products.

fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

Ultra-high grade, premium New Zealand MGOâ„¢ 950+ Manuka Honey. Certified for natural methylglyoxal content (minimum 950mg/kg) - scientifically proven to be a key natural compound in Manuka honey. MGOâ„¢ 950+ Manuka Honey has a delicious rich bitter-sweet flavour and a smooth, creamy, velvety texture.

Warnings

Not suitable for infants under 12 months.

Ingredients

100% New Zealand MGO 950+ Manuka Honey

Directions

Our MGO Manuka Honey can easily fit into your self-care routine. The best way to enjoy it is right off the spoon or mixed in warm water. It also makes a great replacement for refined sugar in warm drinks, as well as the perfect accompaniment to breakfast foods and smoothies. Our MGO Manuka Honey also makes a great natural boost before or after a workout, as well as a wholesome addition to kid's lunches. Avoid exposure to high heat to protect the natural properties.

General Information

The Ultra HD Matte Lipcolor™ formula you know and love, now in 6 NEW nude shades for you.

Delivering creamy, barely there all-day comfort and high coverage colour in the Ultra HD Matte Lipcolor™ signature soft matte finish. Introducing 6 NEW nude shades for you.

For external use only

fields.#productname: Medela Solo Single Electric Breast Pump
fields.cwh-path: Personal Care/Baby Care/Baby Accessories/Medela/Medela Breast Pumps
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

• Easy to use: 4-button intuitive interface and 9 pre-programmed settings.
• Easy to assemble and clean thanks to few parts.
• Lightweight and compact design.
• Improved mobility: built-in rechargeable battery for up to 6 pumping sessions on one full charge.
• Faster charging with USB type C port, compared to micro-USB port.
• 2-Phase Expression® technology mimics your baby's natural sucking rhythm1, 2.
• PersonalFit FlexTM breast shield for increased comfort and 11.8% more milk3.
• Noticeably quieter compared to the previous generation, with less than 45 dB at the Maximum Expression Level.
• Closed system prevents breast milk from entering the tubing

Intuitive and hassle-free.
Solo ™ , the effortlessly easy pump to use.. It has only a few parts making is easy to clean and assemble. With its intuitive 4-button interface and 9 pre-programmed settings this single electric breast pump is extremely easy to use.

Pump wherever you are, even if no power outlet available.
With the cutting-edge available USB type C connector on the Solo ™ single electric breast pump, the built-in rechargeable battery charges faster compared to the micro USB port, lasting for up to six pumping sessions when fully charged.
2-Phase Expression® technology. During a feeding session, babies start by using short, fast sucks to stimulate the Milk Ejection Reflex. Once the milk begins to flow, babies change to a slower, individual rhythm. Medela's 2-Phase Expression® technology mimics baby’s natural sucking rhythms – faster to stimulate milk flow, then slower to provide optimal milk flow.

PersonalFit Flex™ breast shield.
With a 105-degree opening angle, soft rim and oval shape for a better fit, the PersonalFit FlexTM breast shield puts less pressure on your milk ducts than traditional breast shields, resulting in a more effective and comfortable pumping experience. More comfort for you, up to 11.8% more milk for your baby – clinically proven..

Closed system prevents breast milk from entering the tubing, overflowing and leaking into the pump mechanism. This helps ensure that your expressed milk stays safe and clean, but also that your pump's components are protected from potential damage.

Common Uses

Expressing breastmilk

Ingredients

1 x Solo ™ motor unit
1 x 150 ml bottle with lid
1 x bottle stand
1 x PersonalFit Flex™ connector
1 x PersonalFit Flex™ breast shield size 24 mm
1 x USB charging cable
1 x USB power adapter
1 x Instructions for use for Solo ™

fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

The perfect 24-hour set with one ORIGINAL soother and one NIGHT soother, which glows in the dark. With gentle-on-skin SensoPearls™.

At Medela Baby we know soothers can comfort your little one during the day and at sleep time. With the DAY & NIGHT set, you have a dedicated soother for both moments at hand. Both are gentle on skin and loved by nine out of ten babies1! The NIGHT soother has a glow-in-the-dark knob that allows you and your little one to find it in the dark. Without a ring, your baby's sleep is not disturbed when moving at night.

Get the lash extension effect without the commitment

Rimmel Wonder'Extension Mascara is a lash-lengthening mascara that gives the effect of lash extensions, leaving full, long and defined lashes. Formula is built with stretchy texture extends beyond the tips of your lashes. Lash grabbing brush lifts and extends as it lengthens. Clump-free, long lasting, smudge-proof, flake-proof and easy to remove.

Size: 11mL

KEY FEATURES

• Lash extension effect: full, long and defined lashes
• New formula with stretchy texture extends beyond the tips of your lashes
• Clump-free, long lasting, smudge-proof, flake-proof, easy to remove

fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

The perfect 24-hour set with one ORIGINAL soother and one NIGHT soother, which glows in the dark. With gentle-on-skin SensoPearls™.

At Medela Baby we know soothers can comfort your little one during the day and at sleep time. With the DAY & NIGHT set, you have a dedicated soother for both moments at hand. Both are gentle on skin and loved by nine out of ten babies1! The NIGHT soother has a glow-in-the-dark knob that allows you and your little one to find it in the dark. Without a ring, your baby's sleep is not disturbed when moving at night.

Suitable For: 6-18 Mth

Size: 2 Pack

KEY FEATURES

• Orthodontic: Flat, symmetric teat for free tongue movement. Thin shaft minimises space between upper and lower jaws
• Glow in the dark: Easy to find in the dark for you and baby
• Lightweight: Less stress on orofacial muscles
• Sensopearls™: Enhance the airflow between your baby skin and the shield
• Swiss Quality: Developed with experts and made with love in Switzerland
• High Acceptance: 9 out of 10 babies love it
• Ergonomic Shape: To smell mum's comforting scent
• Made without BPA and BPS

fields.#productname: VitalStrength Pre Workout Powder Nuclear Grape 225g
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

Vital Strengths new Pre Workout offers explosive energy, focus and strength to maximise your workout results. Take one scope to assess tolerance, move to two scopes if required. Available in 5 delicious flavours Watermelon Smash, Pineapple Punch, Nuclear Grape, Raspberry Rush & Mango Lemonade.

Warnings

"THIS PRODUCT MAY NOT BE RIGHT FOR YOU. ALWAYS READ THE LABEL, WARNINGS AND INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE, BEFORE PURCHASE. VITAMIN AND MINERAL SUPPLEMENTS SHOULD NOT REPLACE A BALANCED DIET. "

Common Uses

Consume 30 mins prior to your workout for the extra energy boost to get you in the gym or training.

Ingredients

L-Arginine, Tri Creatine Malate, Beta Alanine, Beta Alanine, L-citrulline, L-Tyrosine, L-Leucine, L-Isoleucine, L-Valine, L-Glutamine, Taurine, L-Carnitine Tartrate, Caffeine Glucuronolactone, Folic Acid, Magnesium Citrate, Zinc Gluconate, Vit B3, Vit B5, Vit B6, Vit B12, Vit C Maltodextrin, Citric acid, Stabiliser (466), Silicon dioxide, Sucralose, Acesulphame Potassium, Colour (129), Flavours, Ginger, Ascorbic acid. Contains Soy Lecithin.

Directions

"Mix 9g (approx. 1 scoop) into 200ml of cold water and stir until dissolved."

fields.#productname: Omron HEM7361T Blood Pressure + AFIB Monitor Bluetooth
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

Omron HEM7361T Advanced with AFIB Indicator Blood Pressure Monitor is a great first step to detect any abnormalities in your heart rhythm and in your blood pressure, from the comfort of your home.

The Omron HEM7361T Advanced with AFIB Indicator Blood Pressure Monitor measures and detects blood pressure and AFIB at the same time. Dual Check for Dual Users allows users to have a comprehensive check for their risk of stroke with one device, in one sitting. Designed with families in mind, the dual user function allows for the storage and transmission of measurement data of 2 separate users to their smartphones.



Features:

• AFIB Indicator (Atrial Fibrillation)

• Bluetooth® Connectivity: iPhone/Android

• 2 Users x 100 Reading Memory Each

• Hypertension Indicator

• Cuff Wrapping Guide

• Body Movement Detection

• Irregular Heartbeat Indicator

• 360° IntelliWrap™ Cuff (Medium to Large)

• Average of Last Three Readings

• Large LCD Display

• Carry Bag

• Export readings via the App

• OMRON connect App Compatible

Boxed Contents: Monitor, IntelliWrapTM Cuff, storage case, 4 x AA batteries, instruction manual, Omron connect setup guide

Warnings

Please read all Safety Warnings provided with the product prior to using.

Always read & follow the instructions for use & health warnings. For people with high blood pressure, Consult your doctor to evaluate the readings. Check your device periodically for accuracy.

The device is not intended to diagnose Afib. A diagnosis of Afib can only be confirmed by Electrocardiogram (ECG). If the Afib symbol appears, consult your doctor.

Directions

Please read the full Instructions for Use provided with the product prior to using.
• Avoid bathing, drinking alcohol/caffeine, smoking, exercising and eating for 30 minutes before taking a measurement
• Rest for at least 5 minutes before taking the measurement
• If using the Bluetooth® function you will need to SYNC the device to your smartphone
• Sit upright on a chair with your legs uncrossed and feet flat on the floor, with your back and arm being supported
• Remove tight-fitting clothing from your arm. Do not roll up a tight sleeve. Do not place the arm cuff over thick clothes
• Wrap the arm cuff firmly in place around the left upper arm. Please see instruction manual if needing to use the right arm.
• Positioning the monitor with the START/STOP button towards the body makes it easier to use the device
• The bottom edge of the arm cuff should be 1 to 2 cm above your elbow
• Rest your arm on a table so that the arm cuff is at the same level as your heart
• Ensure solid connection of the air plug and cuff to main unit
• Ensure you remain still and do not talk during the measurement
• Press the START/STOP button
• The cuff will inflate and a result will display on the screen (approx. 30-60 secs)
• The reading will be automatically saved in the memory

fields.#productname: Rimmel Wonder Extension Mascara 001 Very Black
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

Get the lash extension effect without the commitment

Rimmel Wonder'Extension Mascara is a lash-lengthening mascara that gives the effect of lash extensions, leaving full, long and defined lashes. Formula is built with stretchy texture extends beyond the tips of your lashes. Lash grabbing brush lifts and extends as it lengthens. Clump-free, long lasting, smudge-proof, flake-proof and easy to remove.

Size: 11mL

KEY FEATURES

• Lash extension effect: full, long and defined lashes
• New formula with stretchy texture extends beyond the tips of your lashes
• Clump-free, long lasting, smudge-proof, flake-proof, easy to remove
• Dermatologist & ophthalmologist tested

Ingredients

AQUA/WATER/EAU, GLYCERYL STEARATE, PARAFFIN, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, PVP, COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA/COPERNICIA CERIFERA (CARNAUBA) WAX/CIRE DE CARNAUBA, STEARIC ACID, VP/EICOSENE COPOLYMER, POLYSORBATE 20, ARGININE, CERA ALBA/BEESWAX/CIRE D'ABEILLE, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, AMMONIUM ACRYLATES COPOLYMER, HYDROXYETHYLCELLULOSE, PHENOXYETHANOL, PANTHENOL, LAUROYL LYSINE, RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL, BIS-STEARYL DIMETHICONE, SODIUM POLYACRYLATE, NYLON-6/12, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, NYLON-6, ETHYLENE/ACRYLIC ACID COPOLYMER, ALCOHOL DENAT., STYRENE/ACRYLATES COPOLYMER, CELLULOSE, DISODIUM EDTA, DISODIUM DECETH-6 SULFOSUCCINATE, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, STEARALKONIUM HECTORITE, LAURETH-30, C11-15 PARETH-40, C11-15 PARETH-7, PROPYLENE CARBONATE, PANTOLACTONE, SODIUM DEHYDROACETATE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, SODIUM LAURETH-12 SULFATE, DISODIUM PHOSPHATE, POLYSORBATE 60, SILICA, TOCOPHEROL, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, TRIETHOXYCAPRYLYLSILANE

Directions

For best results apply two coats- apply one coat and let it partially dry, then apply another to let the polymers build and stretch beyond the tips of the lashes

fields.#productname: OGX Sea Salt Waves Conditioner 385ml
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
Information

Drag to spin

General Information

From Bondi to Broome, this beach-inspired blend with sea salt, sea kelp and aloe extract helps to rehydrate and condition parched strands. This texturizing formula helps add body and create the look of tousled beach hair all year round. Extend those beach vibes no matter the season with the scent of ocean air and sea salt in your hair!

Why you want it... For hair that gives you all the beach vibes!

Size: 385mL

Scent: Sea Salt Waves

Warnings

Avoid contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately. In case of any discomfort, please discontinue and consult a physician. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Water, Behentrimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Fragrance, PPG-3 Benzyl Ether Myristate, Sodium Benzoate, Steareth-20, Dimethicone, Disodium EDTA, Citric Acid, Polyquaternium-47, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Macrocystis Pyrifera (Kelp) Extract, Maltodextrin/VP Copolymer, PVP, Sea Salt, Sodium Hydroxide.

Directions

What You Do... After shampooing, apply conditioner generously to hair, working through to ends. Wait 3-5 minutes. Rinse hair thoroughly. For best results, use in conjunction with other OGX products.

fields.#productname: Swisse Womens Supergreens+ Powder 120g
fields.cwh-html-ENG:
General Information

Swisse Women's Supergreens+ Powder is a premium quality, great tasting all-in-one daily health supplement with a blend of 46 nutrients to support women's general health and wellbeing, and energy production.

Women's General Health & Wellbeing: Contains a blend of 46 superfoods, fruits, vegetables, vitamins, herbs and antioxidants to maintain general health and wellbeing in women.

Antioxidants: Antioxidants help decrease free radical damage to body cells.

Size: 120g

Warnings

The recommended daily amount of vitamin A from all sources is 700 mcg/RE for women and 900 mcg/RE for men.

This medicine contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 micograms for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded.

Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice.

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
WARNING: If you are pregnant, or considering becoming pregnant, do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 mcg/RE, vitamin A can cause birth defects.
Mix 1 heaped teaspoon (4g) to 150 mL of water or a smoothie. Consume once daily, during or immediatly after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Once dissolved, consume immediately. Some settling of the powder may occur after mixing, for best dissolution of the product, use a protein shaker or blender to mix thoroughly.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.

fields.#productname: Cancer Council SPF 50+ Kids 35ml Tube
fields.cwh-path: Personal Care/Sun Care/Sunscreen, Lotions & Gels/Cancer Council Australia/Cancer Council - Kids
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Dermatologically tested, paraben and fragrance-free lotion for delicate skin.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Caution: Not suitable for babies under 6 months old. Avoid contact with eyes and broken or damaged skin. Patch Test: When using a sunscreen for the first time, test on a small section of skin first. If irritation occurs, rinse thoroughly with water, discontinue use immediately and seek medical advice if required. Check and follow the ‘use by' date stated on the packaging and store sunscreen below 30°C.

Common Uses

SPF50+ broad spectrum protection Specially-formulated and dermatologically tested for delicate skin A gentle forumla that is paraben and fragrance free Tested for 4 hours water resistance. Cancer Council recommends reapplying every 2 hours. Made in Australia

Ingredients

Actives: 4-Methylbenzylidene Camphor 4% w/w, Octocrylene 4% w/w, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane 3% w/w, Ethylhexyl Triazone 3% w/w Preservatives: Octanohydroxamic Acid, Caprylyl Glycol, Glycerol

Directions

For adults, apply at least one teaspoon (5mL) of sunscreen to each arm, leg, front of the body, back of the body and face (including the neck and ears). One full body application should be the equivalent of seven teaspoons (35mL). Reapply regularly: Every TWO HOURS and immediately after swimming, ssweating or towel drying. Apply to dry, clean skin and rub in 20 minutes before heading outside. Use 5 methods of sun protection: PROTECTIVE CLOTHING, EYEWEAR/SUNGLASSES, a BROAD-BRIM HAT and SHADE. Apply sunscreen to remaining exposed areas of skin. Avoid prolonged sun exposure and never rely on sunscreen alone, nor to extend your family's time in the sun Important note: To ensure adequate protection, Cancer Council recommends all sunscreens be re-applied every 2 hours or immediately after swimming, sweating or towel drying.

Indications

fields.#productname: Audiplugs Soft Silicone Comfort 3 Pairs
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Silicone Ear Plugs, Adult size, 3 pairs

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Store out of reach of children. There is a risk of choking if the plug is stuck in the windpipe.

Common Uses

25 dbl, Stop water from entering the Ear Canal. Also suited for sensitive skin types

Ingredients

Silicone

Directions

Instruction for Insertion:
1. Make sure the skin surrounding the ear canal is clean and dry.
2. With clean hands, roll and shape the plug into a “ball”.
3. Place the “ball” against the opening of the ear canal and press so that a smaller portion of it is pressed into the ear canal. Flatten out the rest of the plug on the outside of the opening so that it sticks to the skin and seals around the opening of the ear canal (see illustration).
Please note: Do not shape or divide the plug in a way that allows the plug to enter deeper into the ear canal. A plug that has been pressed in too deep may divide inside the canal and be difficult to remove.

Indications

fields.#productname: Atkins Endulge Single Caramel Nut Chew 34g
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Guilt-free treats. Just like traditional favourites - without the sugar-fuelled carbohydrates. Chocolate, caramel and peanut avour, low carb, low sugar bar with 33% milk chocolate (contains 38% cocoa derivatives) and sweetener. No added sugar, contains naturally occurring sugars. This product contains over 75% less carbohydrates and sugars than regular chocolate, caramel and peanut avoured bars.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Contains peanuts, soy, milk. May contain other tree nuts, wheat, sesame seeds. Excessive consumption may cause a laxative effect.

Common Uses

Makes a perfect low carb snack during your break to keep your weight loss goals on track.

Ingredients

Chocolate 33% (maltitol, chocolate mass, cocoa butter, sodium caseinate, milk fat, emulsifier [soy lecithin], sweetener [sucralose], flavourings, salt), caramel flavoured layer 26% (inulin, polydextrose, water, butter [cream, salt], vegetable fat, nonfat dry milk, emulsifier [soy lecithin], salt, sweetener [sucralose], flavouring), roasted peanuts 14%, maltitol syrup, protein blend (whey protein isolate, milk protein isolate), butter (cream, salt), peanut butter (peanuts, emulsifier [mono and diglycerides], salt, antioxidant [mixed tocopherols]), inulin, flavouring, sweetener (sucralose).

Directions

Store in a dry, cool place, away from direct sunlight. For best before see: Panel. Suitable for All phases of the new Atkins Nutritional Approach. Visit www.atkins.com for more info and weight management tools.

fields.#productname: Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturising Hand Mask 1 Pair
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturising Hand Mask enriched with prebiotic oat & shea butter. It helps repair extra dry skin.

Indulge your hands in our easy to use, non-drip Skin Relief Hand Mask. These gloves are designed to help restore essential moisture to extra dry skin. They are infused with a nourishing formula that helps balance skin's natural moisture barrier, containing shea butter and prebiotic oat known to have soothing and nourishing properties, leaving your hands visibly soft, smooth and healthy looking.

- No added Paraben.
- Fragrance free.
- Formulated to be gentle enough for sensitive skin.
- Dermatologist recommended brand.

Product Claims: No added Paraben. Fragrance free. Dermatologist recommended.

Recommended By: Dermatologist.

Boxed Contents: 2 single-use gloves

Size: 1 Pack

Scent: Prebiotic oat & shea butter

Fragrance Free?: Yes

Dermatologist Recommended?: Yes

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Common Uses

Ingredients

Water, Glycerin, Distearyldimonium Chloride, Petrolatum, Isopropyl Palmitate, Cetyl Alcohol, Dimethicone, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Flour, Benzyl Alcohol, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Oil, Steareth-20, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Chloride, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Extract.

Directions

Step 1: Wash hands thoroughly and dry.
Step 2: Insert one hand in each glove and fasten the strap for comfort. Wear as you would any other glove and enjoy some well-deserved me-time!
Step 3: Remove after 10 minutes. No need to rinse.
Step 4: Massage remaining product into skin until fully absorbed.

fields.#productname: Atkins Endulge Single Milk Chocolate 30g
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Guilt-free treats. Just like traditional favourites - without the sugar-fuelled carbohydrates. Low carb, low sugar, milk chocolate bar (contains 37% cocoa derivates), with sweetener. No added sugar, contains naturally occurring sugars. This product contains over 75% less carbohydrates and sugars than regular milk chocolate.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Contains milk and soy. May contain peanuts, tree nuts, gluten, sesame and sulphites. Excessive consumption may cause a laxative effect.

Common Uses

Makes a perfect low carb snack during your break to keep your weight loss goals on track.

Ingredients

Cocoa butter, maltitol, polydextrose, milk solids, cocoa mass, emulsifiers (soy lecithin, 476), flavour, sweetener (sucralose)

Directions

Store in a dry, cool place, away from direct sunlight. For best before see: Panel. Suitable for All phases of the new Atkins Nutritional Approach. Visit www.atkins.com for more info and weight management tools.

Indications

fields.#productname: Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturising Foot Mask 1 Pair
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturising Foot Mask enriched with prebiotic oat & shea butter. It helps repair extra dry skin.

Indulge your feet in our easy to use, non-drip Skin Relief Foot Mask. These slippers are designed to help restore essential moisture to extra dry skin. They are infused with a nourishing formula that helps balance skin's natural moisture barrier, containing shea butter and prebiotic oat known to have soothing and nourishing properties, leaving your skin visibly soft, smooth and healthy looking.

- No added Paraben.
- Fragrance free.
- Formulated to be gentle enough for sensitive skin.

Product Claims: No added Paraben. Fragrance free. Dermatologist recommended.

Recommended By: Dermatologist.

Boxed Contents: 2 single-use slippers

Size: 1 Pack

Scent: rebiotic oat & shea butter

Fragrance Free?: Yes

Dermatologist Recommended?: Yes

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Common Uses

Ingredients

Water, Glycerin, Distearyldimonium Chloride, Petrolatum, Isopropyl Palmitate, Cetyl Alcohol, Dimethicone, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Flour, Benzyl Alcohol, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Oil, Steareth-20, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Chloride, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Extract.

Directions

Step 1: Wash feet thoroughly and dry.
Step 2: Insert one foot in each slipper and fasten the strap for comfort. Sit back and enjoy some well-deserved me-time!
Step 3: Remove after 10 minutes. No need to rinse.
Step 4: Massage remaining product into skin until fully absorbed.

Indications

fields.#productname: BSc High Protein Bar Rocky Road 60g
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

A seriously delicious high-protein bar that's actually good for you? It does exist! The perfect convenient and nutritious treat that's low in carbs and contains no artificial flavours or sweetners. Pop one in your bag to fight afternoons cravings, satisfy the sweet tooth or get your protein hit on-the-go. Choose from a range of incredible flavours: Cookie Dough, Choc Mint, Rocky Road, Cookies & Cream & Salted Caramel.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Made on Equipment which processes Peanuts, Tree Nuts & Sesame, therefore these allergens may be present. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect

Common Uses

Snacking, for those on the go. An ideal post-workout protein hit, craving crusher or healthy treat.

Ingredients

BSc Protein Blend (Dairy Protein Blend [Whey Protein Concentrate, Whey Protein Isolate, Calcium Caseinate], Soy Protein Isolate, Soy Protein Nuggets), No Added Sugar Milk Protein Chocolate (18%) (Maltitol, Cocoa Solids [33%], Milk Solids [20%], Soy Protein Isolate, Emulsifiers [Soy Lecithin, Polyglycerol Polyricinoleate], Natural Vanilla Flavour), Polydextrose, Maltitol, Berry Paste (7%) (Concentrated Apple Puree [31%], Cherry Puree [6%], Concentrated Elderberry Juice [0.8%], Humectant [Sorbitol, Glycerol], Invert Sugar, Bulking Agent [Polydextrose], Sunflower Oil, Wheat Fibre, Gelling Agent [Pectin], Natural Flavour, Firming Agent [Calcium Lactate], Acidity Regulator [Citric Acid]), Sorbitol, Humectant (Glycerol), Glycine, Cocoa Powder, Sunflower Oil, Coconut (1.5%), Pistachios (1.5%), Berry Bites (1.5%), Natural Flavour, Stevia Extract, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Salt, Natural Colour (Carmine), Antioxidant (Mixed Tocopherols).

Directions

Use as an in between meal snack or post workout.

Indications

fields.#productname: BSc High Protein Bar Choc Mint 60g
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

A seriously delicious high-protein bar that's actually good for you? It does exist! The perfect convenient and nutritious treat that's low in carbs and contains no artificial flavours or sweetners. Pop one in your bag to fight afternoons cravings, satisfy the sweet tooth or get your protein hit on-the-go. Choose from a range of incredible flavours: Cookie Dough, Choc Mint, Rocky Road, Cookies & Cream & Salted Caramel.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Made on Equipment which processes Peanuts, Tree Nuts & Sesame, therefore these allergens may be present. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect

Common Uses

Snacking, for those on the go. An ideal post-workout protein hit, craving crusher or healthy treat.

Ingredients

BSc Protein Blend (Dairy Protein Blend [Whey Protein Concentrate, Whey Protein Isolate, Calcium Caseinate], Soy Protein Isolate), No Added Sugar Protein Chocolate (Maltitol, Cocoa Solids [33%], Milk Solids [20%], Soy Protein Isolate, Emulsifiers [Soy Lecithin, Polyglycerol Polyricinoleate], Natural Vanilla Flavour), Polydextrose, Maltitol, Humectant (Glycerol), Sorbitol, Vanilla Paste, Glycine, Sugar Free Mint Chips (2.5%), Sunflower Oil, Soy Protein Nuggets, Cocoa Powder (1.5%), Stevia Extract, Natural Flavour, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Salt, Antioxidant (Mixed Tocopherols).

Directions

Use as an in between meal snack or post workout.

fields.#productname: Biore Brightening Clay Mask 47g
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Biore Yuzu Lemon + Papaya Brightening Clay Mask - Lifts dead skin cells and boosts radiance to improve tone and texture, for brighter skin in 1 week* Yuzu Lemon is a known source of Vitamin C, known for its ability to balance and brighten Papaya contains natural enzymes known to smooth skin by removing dead skin buildup

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

Warning: For external use only. Keep out of reach of children. Not a food. Do not ingest.

Common Uses

Specially formulated with our proven Japanese technology and AHA fruit acid, this unique mask lifts dead skin cells and surface debris while brightening the look of skin for a smoother and more radient complexion

Ingredients

Ingredients : Aqua, Kaolin, Glycerin, Cetyl Alcohol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Mica, Sodium Hydroxide, Disodium EDTA, Ascorbic Acid, Citric Acid, Tromethamine, Lactobacillus/Papaya Fruit Ferment Extract, Malic Acid, Leuconostoc/Radish Root Ferment Filtrate, Citrus Junos Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Benzoate, CI 15510, CI 77891

Directions

WET FACE. To apply mask, squeeze a generous amount of product onto fingertips and spread evenly across face, avoiding the eye area. Allow mask to sit on skin for 3-5 minutes. Feeling a little tingle? Don't worry, that's the mask hard at work! REMOVE AND REFRESH: Wet face and rinse thoroughly. If needed use a washcloth. Use 2-3 times per week.

Indications

fields.#productname: Blooms Kids Probiotic Toothpaste Flavour Free 50g
fields.cwh-path: Personal Care/Oral Hygiene and Dental Care/Toothpaste
fields.cwh-html:
Information

General Information

Henry Blooms Kids Probiotic Toothpaste is full of natural goodies with none of the nasties to keep little mouths fresh and clean. Unique oral probiotic ingredients Dental-Lac™ works together with Xylitol to clean the teeth and gums, promote healthy oral flora and fight non-beneficial bacteria.

Miscellaneous

Drug Interactions

Warnings

This product is safe if swallowed but not recommended.

Common Uses

Henry Blooms Kids Probiotic Toothpaste is full of natural goodies with none of the nasties to keep little mouths fresh and clean.

Ingredients

Glycerin, Water, Hydrated
Silica, Sorbitol, Calcium Carbonate, Xylitol, Xanthan Gum, Cocos nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Sodium Lauroyl Sarcosinate, Sodium Benzoate,
Aloe barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice, Lactobacillus paracasei GMNL-33 (Dental-LacTM), Carbomer.

Directions

Brush gently in a circular motion twice a day. Rinse and spit out after brushing.

Indications
